                                  <CheckCircle2 size={14} className="mt-0.5 text-green-300"/> 
                                  <span><strong>Diet:</strong> Eat warm, home-cooked meals. Avoid raw papaya, pineapple, and excessive caffeine.</span>
                              </li>
                              <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
